'''Hamid Bénani''' ( yavutse ku ya 5 Ugushyingo 1940), ni [[Maroke|umuyobozi wa firime muri Maroc]], umwanditsi wa sinema akaba n'umukinnyi wa sinema.  Umwe mu bahanzi bubahwa cyane muri [[Maroc]], Bénani yakoze filime nyinshi zamamaye cyane nka ''Wechma'', ''La prière des absents'' na ''L'enfant Cheïkh'' .  Ni n'umuproducer, umwanditsi n'umwanditsi.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 5 Ugushyingo 1940 iMeknes, muri [[Maroke|Maroc]] . Yize idini mu ishuri rya Koran. Nyuma, yarangije amashuri yisumbuye muri Poeymirau na Moulay Ismaïl yisumbuye. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1958, Bénani yakiriye imyitozo mu ikinamico n'amahugurwa yo guhanga no kwandika yateguwe na Minisiteri y'Urubyiruko na Siporo. Hanyuma mu 1964, yagiye mu ishami ry’amabaruwa ya Rabat kugira ngo abone uruhushya muri filozofiya. Mu 1965, yatangiye kwiga amafilime muri Institut des hautes études cinématographiques (IDHEC) aho yahawe mu 1967 mu gice cyitwa "Direction, production and management". Hagati aho, yitabiriye amahugurwa y’ikinamico yabereye i Sorbonne no muri EPHE2 yakozwe nabafilozofe Jacques Derrida,Roland Barthes na Paul Ricœur

Mu 1968, Bénani yinjiye kuri Televiziyo ya [[Maroc]]. Nyuma yaje kuba umuyobozi w'ishami rishinzwe ububanyi n'amahanga. Mu 1969, yeguye kuri Société Nationale de Radiodiffusion et de Télévision (RTM). Mu 1970, yashinze isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa yitwa ''Sigma 3'' ku bufatanye na Ahmed Bouanani,Mohamed Abderrahman Tazi na Mohamed Sekkat. Muri uwo mwaka, isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa yakoze firime yambere ya ''Wechma'' .  Iyi filime yerekanwe muri federasiyo y’amahuriro y’amafirime ya [[Maroc]] (FMCC) kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi ndetse n’ishimwe mu minsi mikuru ya firime, aho iyi filime ifatwa nk’amafilime yashinze ya sinema ya [[Maroc]].  

Nubwo iyi filime yakunzwe cyane mu banegura, Bénani yagombaga gutegereza imyaka igera kuri makumyabiri kugira ngo ayobore filime ye ya kabiri yakinnye, ''La prière des absents (Isengesho'' ry'Abadahari), ku ikubitiro yiswe 'Amabanga y'inzira y'amata'. Iyi filime yakuwe mu gitabo kizwi cyane cyanditswe n'umwanditsi Tahar Ben Jelloun.  Mu 2011, yayoboye filime ''L'enfant Cheïkh'' . Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya Tangier kandi ryakiriwe neza n’abari bitabiriye ibirori. Kandi film yatsindiye igihembo kumashusho meza. 

Usibye icyerekezo, yasohoye igitabo yise "Le dernier chant des insoumises" (Indirimbo ya nyuma y'inyeshyamba) munsi y'ibendera rya Editions du Sirocco.  Igitabo cyatsindiye igihembo cya Grand Atlas muri 2019. 

